Subject: [PATCH v7 18/26] PM / devfreq: rockchip-dfi: account for multiple DDRMON_CTRL registers
Date:   Tue,  4 Jul 2023 11:32:34 +0200
Message-Id: <20230704093242.583575-19-s.hauer@pengutronix.de>
